<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 | Page Not Found</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <div class="border-t-4 border-blue-500 w-full"></div>
    <div class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-md w-full p-6">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-50 rounded-full h-64 w-64">
                        <span class="text-9xl font-bold text-blue-500">404</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Oops! Page Not Found</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                    Sorry, the page you are looking for does not exist.<br>
                    It might have been moved, deleted, or you may have typed the address incorrectly.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>